name: DispatchQoS.QoSClass
desc: Quality-of-service classes that specify the priorities for executing tasks.

items.name: case userInteractive
items.desc: The quality-of-service class for user-interactive tasks, such as animations, event handling, or updating your app's user interface.

items.name: case userInitiated
items.desc: The quality-of-service class for tasks that prevent the user from actively using your app.

items.name: case utility
items.desc: The quality-of-service class for tasks that the user does not track actively.

items.name: case background
items.desc: The quality-of-service class for maintenance or cleanup tasks that you create.

items.name: case unspecified
items.desc: The absence of a quality-of-service class.
